{"name":"Wahnsinn","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"Legt die Auswirkungen des Wahnsinns fest.","results":[{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[1,20],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"2XIIkodnuCLsKNV8","text":"Der Charakter zieht sich in seinen Geist zurück und ist gelähmt. Der Effekt endet, wenn der Charakter Schaden erleidet.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[21,30],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"dqpfr30XGaaovqOe","text":"Der Charakter wird kampfunfähig und verbringt die Dauer schreiend, lachend oder weinend.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[31,40],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"16Bn8GICA49J9r3K","text":"Der Charakter wird verängstigt und muss seine Aktion und Bewegung in jeder Runde dafür aufwenden, vor der Quelle der Angst zu fliehen.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[41,50],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"qVQ27JeGrpHzd7XB","text":"Der Charakter beginnt zu brabbeln und ist unfähig, normal zu sprechen oder zu zaubern.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[51,60],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"yxqtgGMMkcn1pt6w","text":"Der Charakter muss seine Aktion in jeder Runde dafür aufwenden, die am nächsten befindliche Kreatur anzugreifen.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[61,70],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"SIzu4DHwVbqdK61u","text":"Der Charakter erlebt wilde Halluzinationen und hat einen Nachteil auf Attributswürfe.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[71,75],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"FWcGAJP2wO8MUxDj","text":"Der Charakter tut alles, was irgendjemand ihm befiehlt, sofern es nicht offensichtlich selbstzerstörerisch ist.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[76,80],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"ubsWn0AsZehhHkPc","text":"Der Charakter wird von dem Drang übermannt, etwas Merkwürdiges zu essen, wie Dreck, Schleim oder Abfall.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[81,90],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"PjzBiSHW9RLlDUId","text":"Der Charakter ist betäubt.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}},{"type":0,"weight":1,"range":[91,100],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","_id":"4GDDLGp8lw4dU4Hn","text":"Der Charakter wird bewusstlos.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","documentId":null,"flags":{}}],"formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.2","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1691945596650,"modifiedTime":1691946055699,"lastModifiedBy":"YzL2W1htQr2gHsBA"},"_id":"Gu0MpKvlUBzDrTzo"}
